{"tid":1895433,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"呍 呢 拿 新 地 宣 佈 暫 別 麥 當 勞","createTime":"2020-02-24T14:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:50:00.000Z","uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0506abd1b540d9d947a59711b3d246b210b9b2df","tid":1895433,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/1024/202002/20200224185502_2_1582541702.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2F1024%2F202002%2F20200224185502_2_1582541702.png&h=600fb279&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2556aa2ef979be463feac638c24ba65f8826128","tid":1895433,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:03:28.000Z","msg":"【號外！呍呢拿新地宣佈暫別麥記 】<br />\n<br />\n作為麥當勞經典滋味咁多年，呍呢拿新地呢幾年都攰喇，所以決定放個大假，畀啲機會後輩：由<span style=\"color: red;\">福岡草莓</span>上陣！<br />\n<br />\n而家嚟食新地筒、麥旋風、新地&hellip;全部都有福岡草莓味。而且全線麥當勞都有得歎，仲可以揀埋朱古力脆皮添！<br />\n<br />\n#麥當勞 #呍呢拿新地 #暫停供應 #福岡草莓 #登陸全線麥當勞 #有脆皮 #冇脆皮 #大窩夫筒 #3杯THX"},{"pid":"c54caa70786d79df7d4e9cac40466f52227d8830","tid":1895433,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/1024/202002/20200224185458_0_1582541698.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2F1024%2F202002%2F20200224185458_0_1582541698.png&h=d7d6603a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92fe584bcd117e20aa93db65df3b7edf44d4d20f","tid":1895433,"uid":286309,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"三萬，thx<br />\n你死啦<br />\n藍絲要擺食你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91f3f68ddfbc5c598a36033fd4fd726e13d635b","tid":1895433,"uid":63675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T14:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: